      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EXACTLY LIKE DAD (8) is in sizzling form lately, rocketing around Healesville in 16.80 to score two back then following on with a 22.24 win over 395m at this track. In form and looks the one to beat again. JAZZY BOO (2) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 6 lengths at this track in a handy 22.74. Speedy beginner who should be prominent early on from an inside box. Leading player again. TOORA GRACIE (1) finds it hard to win but looks close to breaking through. Has hit the frame at her last three runs, the latest finishing third (22.86) at this track. Speedy beginner who should be in the action early off the inside. Bold showing expected. BRISTOL MOSS (5) is a surprise last-start placegetter who should be thereabouts.",
